        "setup": "Go to [Project settings → API Keys](https://console.ory.com/projects/current/developers) in the Ory Console, click **Create new API key**, choose a name and expiration, then copy the one-time secret. The key is project-scoped and is shown only once. Use the `ory_apikey_` or `ory_pat_` value as your bearer token.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
      "ory_workspace_api_key": {
        "type": "api_key",
        "label": "Ory Workspace API key",
        "generateUrl": "https://console.ory.com/",
        "setup": "In the Ory Console, open the workspace menu, go to **Workspace settings** and create an API key. This key authorizes workspace admin APIs and also applies to project admin APIs across projects in that workspace. Copy it once when shown.",
