        "setup": "Configure your MCP client to connect to `https://ory-docs.mcp.kapa.ai`. The Ory docs page indicates Claude Code authenticates in the browser after `claude mcp add --transport http ory-docs https://ory-docs.mcp.kapa.ai` and then running `/mcp`. Other MCP clients may use their own ambient login flow; no separate Ory credential is minted here.",
        "acquisition": "ambient"
